    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/b83a0ca955ba5d7bbc23d01c1fdd432f.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/18056f165ade6e43edafa7a627f33255.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/18056f165ade6e43edafa7a627f33255.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/18056f165ade6e43edafa7a627f33255.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从《反恐精英》著名模组中获得灵感，在各种坡道上冲浪！ <strong>直观的教程</strong>将帮助你学习并掌握这种<strong>独特的机制</strong>，<strong>酷炫的音效设计</strong>让游戏更加有趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/8aed04a46316193475fd2e1f1a67b94d.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/c47734df2071c338f4643b92c069e17e.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/c47734df2071c338f4643b92c069e17e.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/c47734df2071c338f4643b92c069e17e.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你有足够的速度，可以<strong>跳跃</strong>、<strong>二段跳</strong>，甚至<strong>兔子跳</strong>！ 利用它们并明智地选择你的时机来<strong>保持动能</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/484eb9077d5fec6457535f43e4aa071c.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/0717a4edd0256e4047593456e14b60e2.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/0717a4edd0256e4047593456e14b60e2.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/0717a4edd0256e4047593456e14b60e2.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >花时间享受美丽的水彩纹理和神秘的氛围，同时还有一段宁静的 <strong>35 分钟长的原声音乐</strong>。 别忘了探索这个世界来<strong>发现秘密</strong>……不过要小心，有些可能会试图逃脱！ <strong>隐藏角色</strong>可能会透露一些关于你所生活的世界的信息……<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/a3473f83c00f664fafbd364295c5a51e.webp?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=35 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/1d1f2280a514bcbb3dc7b4b970121e3d.poster.avif?t=1770280479\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/1d1f2280a514bcbb3dc7b4b970121e3d.webm?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1280060/extras/1d1f2280a514bcbb3dc7b4b970121e3d.mp4?t=1770280479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >快速击败 <strong>30 多个手工打造的关卡</strong>以赢得奖牌，从<strong>青铜的到黄金的</strong>……如果你有实力，甚至可以<strong>尝试打破我的记录</strong>！ 还可以在<strong>排行榜</strong>上与朋友比较你的时间！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我是一个<strong>独立开发者</strong>，多年来怀着热情制作游戏，希望你会喜欢 Hoverflow，<strong>我的第一个大型项目</strong> 🖤 如果有任何问题，请加入 Discord, 我通常会很快回复! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simon.</p>",
